Grimlock chuckled as Switchblade fell over, but due to him already
heading forward, and the fact that he was not paying attention, received
the laser blast right into his chest. The force sent his body up, so he
was no longer horizontal, but he was still traveling at flying speed. He
hit the wall with a loud crash, and fell over backwards, smoke pouring
out of his hit spot. He hit the ground, with another thud, and growled
while lying there.
